ID of BCM4312 is 0x4315, not 0x4312 and not 0x4313.

0x4312 is BCM4311.

Etc...

I see inconsistency here with https://pci-ids.ucw.cz/v2.2/pci.ids and https://linux-hardware.org/?view=search&vendorid=14e4&deviceid=4315

How card descriptions in this structure are used?
